@startuml
title General Ledger Period Status Lifecycle

hide empty description

state Open as "Open\nRegular postings are allowed."
state SoftClose as "Soft Close\nOnly authorized adjustments are allowed."
state HardClose as "Hard Close\nAll postings are prevented; ready for reporting."
state PermanentClose  as "Permanent Close\nPermanently locked and auditable."

[*] --> Open : Initialize Period

Open --> SoftClose : Initiate Soft Close
Open --> HardClose : Immediate Hard Close

SoftClose --> Open : Reopen Period
SoftClose --> HardClose : Finalize Hard Close

HardClose --> SoftClose : Reopen for Adjustments
HardClose --> PermanentClose : Final Permanent Lock

PermanentClose --> [*] : Locked

@enduml